    "execution_view": "### MONDAY: Legs (Power/Stability) + Core\n- A1. Barbell Back Squats: 4x6-8 | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- B1. Walking Lunges (DB/KB): 3x10-12 reps per leg | Tempo: 2-1-1\n- C1. Bulgarian Split Squats: 3x8-10 reps per leg | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- D1. Weighted GHD Extensions: 3x10 | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- E1. Weighted Planks: 3x60s\n- F1. Zone 2 Cardio: 30-45m (Rower/Bike)\n\n### TUESDAY: Chest & Back + HIIT Finisher\n- A1. Flat Bench Press (BB): 4x8-10 | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- B1. Barbell Rows: 4x8-10 | Tempo: 2-1-2\n- C1. Incline DB Press: 3x10-12 | Tempo: 2-1-1\n- D1. Lat Pulldowns: 3x10-12 | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- E1. FINISHER: \"The Compression\" (15-20m)\n    - Format: 4 Rounds. 60s rest between rounds.\n    - KB Swings (20), Rower Sprint (250m), Burpees (15), Hanging Leg Raises (15)\n\n### THURSDAY: Shoulders & Arms + HIIT Finisher\n- A1. Overhead Press (BB/DB): 4x8-10 | Tempo: 2-1-1\n- B1. Lateral Raises: 3x12-15 | Tempo: 2-1-2\n- C1. Bicep Curls (EZ Bar): 3x10-12 | Tempo: 3-1-1\n- D1. Tricep Pushdowns (Cable): 3x10-12 | Tempo: 2-1-1\n- E1. FINISHER: \"The Engine Burn\" (15m EMOM)\n    - Min 1: 12 Cal Rower (Sprinting)\n    - Min 2: 20 Mountain Climbers\n    - Min 3: 30s Battle Ropes (Max Intensity)\n\n### FRIDAY: Legs & Back (Volume) + Core\n- A1. Goblet Squats (DB/KB): 4x12-15 | Tempo: 3-1-2\n- B1. Weighted Pull-ups: 4x6-8 | Tempo: 3-1-X\n- C1. Leg Extensions: 3x12-15 | Tempo: 2-1-2\n- D1. Seated Cable Rows: 3x12-15 | Tempo: 2-1-2\n- E1. GHD Sit-ups: 3x15\n- F1. THE FINISHER: \"The Genesis Chipper\" (15-12-9-6-3)\n    - Format: For Time. Descending reps for each round.\n    - Devil Presses\n    - Kettlebell Swings\n    - Push Presses\n    - *Total Volume: 45 reps of each movement.*"
